How to run the simulator

./run mapdir/ [arg]

where mapdir/ is the folder where the xml definition of the map is located along with the stripts genTrips.py and simulate.py

Arguments
-u # ---percentage of vehicles using the system
-tp # ---generate new vehicle spawning times from the OD matrix in genTrips.py with # percentage busses 
-c # ---the congestion level, recommend between 0.4 - 2.0. Default is 1.4. Note: only works if tp is given
-g ---system runs as GUI
-n ---rebuild the map
-o ---set output of the test results
